alteches.library.caltech.edu%2F34%2F3%2FFeynmanLosAlamos.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20him%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20complaining%20about%20the%20censors%20watching.%20Officials%20told%20him%20to%20ask%20her%20not%20to%20mention%20censorship.%20When%20he%20did%2C%20they%20returned%20his%20letter%20and%20said%20he%20had%20to%20inform%20her%20without%20mentioning%20censorship%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20in%20the%20heck%20am%20I%20going%20to%20do%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taylorfrancis.com%2Fchapters%2Fedit%2F10.4324%2F9781351302005-11%2Fpapa-bomb-carol-wolkowitz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Los%20Alamos'%20residents%20was%20mid-20s.%20For%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lanl.gov%2Fmuseum%2Fnews%2Fnewsletter%2F2017%2F2017-01%2Fscience-question-babies.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E80%20babies%3C%2Fa%3E%20born%20in%20the%20project's%20first%20year%2C%20the%20same%20P.O.%20box%20number%20where%20their%20mail%20was%20sent%20was%20also%20put%20on%20their%20birth%20certificates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20poem%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FManhattan_Project%2F9v_oDwAAQBAJ%3Fhl%3Den%26gbpv%3D1%26dq%3D%25E2%2580%259CHe%2Bthought%2Byou%2527d%2Bbe%2Bscientific%2B%2F%2BInstead%2Byou%2527re%2Bjust%2Bprolific.%25E2%2580%259D%26pg%3DPA240%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoked%20fun%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Groves'%20annoyance%20at%20the%20number%20of%20newborns%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20thought%20you'd%20be%20scientific%20%2F%20Instead%20you're%20just%20prolific.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20days%2C%20physicist%20Robert%20Serber%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.aip.org%2Faapt%2Fajp%2Farticle%2F88%2F12%2F1175%2F859737%2FManhattan-Project-The-Story-of-the-Century-Bruce%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelivered%20an%20orientation%20lecture%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20about%2030%20people%20about%20the%20project.%20Carpenters%20and%20electricians%20were%20hard%20at%20work.%20When%20Serber%20mentioned%20the%20bomb%2C%20Oppenheimer%20instructed%20John%20Manley%20to%20tell%20Serber%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Bgadget%26quot%3B%20in%20case%20the%20workers%20overheard.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFatigue%20and%20fighting%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20memoirs%20and%20interviews%2C%20some%20scientists'%20wives%20claimed%20not%20to%20have%20known%20what%20their%20husbands%20were%20working%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeon%20Fisher%20brought%20red%20and%20green%20detonator%20casings%20home%20for%20his%20child%20to%20play%20with.%20Phyllis%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20used%20them%20to%20trim%20a%20Christmas%20tree.%20Later%2C%20she%20reflected%20on%20the%20irony%20of%20decorating%20an%20evergreen%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20renewal%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bmessengers%20of%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIgnorance%20had%20sanctioned%20that%20strange%20combination%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnsuworks.nova.edu%2Fpcs%2Fvol15%2Fiss2%2F3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20secrecy%2C%20the%20stress%2C%20and%20the%20long%20hours%20all%20contributed%20to%20a%20tense%20atmosphere%20that%20could%20set%20everyone%20on%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRank%2C%20housing%20assignments%2C%20the%20part%20of%20town%20in%20which%20one%20lived%2C%20social%20invitations%2C%20administrative%20assignments%2C%20everything%20became%20important%2C%20occasionally%20in%20a%20childish%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Emile%20Segr%C3%A9%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublishing.cdlib.org%2Fucpressebooks%2Fview%3FdocId%3Dft700007rb%3Bquery%3D%3Bbrand%3Ducpress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elater%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20atmosphere%20also%20strained%20marriages.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20Leon%20had%20always%20patiently%20described%20his%20scientific%20projects%20or%20research%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Phyllis%20Fisher%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FAtomic_Spaces%2FK0hCRmHYRXEC%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BBut%20this%20time%20he%20made%20it%20absolutely%20clear%20that%20I%20wasn't%20to%20ask%20and%2C%20if%20I%20did%2C%20he%20wasn't%20about%20to%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20especially%20difficult%20when%20their%20husbands%20wouldn't%20come%20home%20at%20night%2C%20Ruth%20Marshak%20later%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Tech%20Area%20was%20a%20great%20pit%20which%20swallowed%20our%20scientist%20husbands%20out%20of%20sight%2C%20almost%20out%20of%20our%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FAtomic_Spaces%2FK0hCRmHYRXEC%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20told%20Elsie%20McMillan%20that%20the%20scientists%20were%20working%20on%20a%20weapon.%20It%20helped%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fahf.nuclearmuseum.org%2Fvoices%2Foral-histories%2Felsie-mcmillans-lecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20better%20understand%20when%20my%20husband%20left%20me%26quot%3B%20and%20why%20they%20all%20%26quot%3Blooked%20so%20drawn%2C%20so%20tired%2C%20so%20worried.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20life%20of%20'hectivity'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Los%20Alamos's%20wealthier%20citizens%2C%20the%20rustic%20conditions%20took%20some%20adjustment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWater%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.aip.org%2Faapt%2Fajp%2Farticle%2F88%