EFed's%20Beige%20Book%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20American%20consumers%20are%20finally%20dialing%20back%20on%20discretionary%20spending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo-called%20%26quot%3Bfun%20and%20games%26quot%3B%20spending%20has%20softened%20in%20areas%20outside%20of%20cruise%20lines%20and%20air%20travel%2C%20Rosenberg%20said%2C%20which%20likely%20spells%20trouble%20for%20the%20economy%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%20YOLO%20purchases%20helped%20prop%20up%20the%20economy%20through%20the%20pandemic%20years%20%E2%80%93%20and%20when%20subtracting%20their%20impact%20over%20the%20last%20four%20quarters%2C%20the%20US%20economy%20was%20%26quot%3Bas%20flat%20as%20a%20pancake%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20experts%20have%20warned%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20already%20starting%20to%20turn%20sluggish.%20Though%20GDP%20grew%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20real%20gross%20domestic%20income%20has%20already%20fallen%20into%20a%20recession%2C%20Rosenberg%20said%2C%20with%20the%20measure%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bea.gov%2Fdata%2Fincome-saving%2Fgross-domestic-income%23%3A~%3Atext%3DReal%2520gross%2520domestic%2520income%2520(GDI%2Cof%2520measuring%2520U.S.%2520economic%2520activity.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshrinking%20over%20the%20last%20two%20quarters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20another%20reason%20to%20suspect%20that%20consumers%20will%20continue%20to%20pull%20back%20on%20bucket%20list%20purchases%20over%20the%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20compared%20the%20current%20economic%20environment%20to%20that%20of%202007%2C%20when%20markets%20falsely%20assumed%20that%20wealth%20generated%20from%20the%20housing%20market%20would%20prevent%20the%20US%20from%20tipping%20into%20a%20recession.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20a%20recession%20is%20not%20here%20yet%20in%20a%20classical%20sense%2C%20to%20say%20that%20the%20business%20cycle%20has%20not%20been%20repealed%20and%20that%20the%20lags%20from%20the%20policy%20interest%20rate%20%E2%80%A6%20isn't%20going%20to%20cause%20a%20recession%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20a%20reckless%20proposition%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20have%20been%20fretting%20over%20a%20potential%20recession%20for%20the%20past%20year%2C%20as%20the%20Fed%20aggressively%20hiked%20interest%20rates%20to%20control%20inflation.%20High%20rates%20threaten%20to%20tip%20the%20economy%20into%20a%20downturn%2C%20experts%20warn%2C%20and%20the%20Fed%20is%20expected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fmarkets%2Finterest-rates%2Fcme-fedwatch-tool.html%3Fredirect%3D%2Ftrading%2Finterest-rates%2Fcountdown-to-fomc.html%5C%22%3Eraise%20interest%20rates%20by%20another%2025%20basis-points%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20conclusion%20of%20its%20policy%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-recession-yolo-spenders-pandemic-stimulus-cash-david-rosenberg-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690313055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58a707d901fe58ae018b5294%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-recession-yolo-spenders-pandemic-stimulus-cash-david-rosenberg-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22YOLO%20spenders%20have%20already%20started%20to%20dial%20back%20on%20their%20bucket%20list%20purchases%2C%20data%20from%20the%20Fed's%20Beige%20Book%20shows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-recession-yolo-spenders-pandemic-stimulus-cash-david-rosenberg-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Dow's%20longest%20win%20streak%20since%202017%20is%20another%20sign%20that%20suggests%20there%20is%20no%20recession%