2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-intends-to-visit-china-in-october%2Famp_articleshow%2F102115207.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-intends-to-visit-china-in-october%2Famp_articleshow%2F102115207.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%20Writes%20To%20Opposition%20MPs%20Over%20Parliament%20Logjam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeeking%20to%20break%20the%20current%20logjam%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Tuesday%20sought%20%26quot%3Binvaluable%20cooperation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20Parliament%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20rise%20above%20party%20lines%20to%20find%20a%20%26quot%3Bpermanent%26quot%3B%20solution%20to%20the%20embroglio%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bharmonious%26quot%3B%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20identical%20letters%20in%20Hindi%20to%20opposition%20leaders%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Shah%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20want%20that%20MPs%20of%20all%20political%20parties%20give%20them%20confidence%20that%20the%20lawmakers%20are%20united%20and%20committed%20to%20the%20peace%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20is%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20Chowdhury%20is%20the%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20the%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20and%20urged%20all%20to%20cooperate%2C%20rising%20above%20party%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Manipur%20was%20experiencing%20a%20new%20era%20of%20peace%20and%20development%20during%20the%20last%20six%20years%20of%20the%20BJP%20rule%20but%20some%20court%20orders%20and%20some%20incidents%20resulted%20in%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20during%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20minister%20said%20some%20%26quot%3Bshameful%20incidents%26quot%3B%20also%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20after%20which%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Northeast%20and%20especially%20Manipur%20are%20expecting%20from%20Parliament%20that%2C%20rising%20above%20party%20lines%2C%20the%20leaders%20will%20stand%20with%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20also%20our%20great%20Parliament%20has%20done%20it.%20The%20opposition%20is%20demanding%20that%20the%20government%20gives%20a%20statement%20but%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20government%20is%20ready%20not%20only%20for%20a%20statement%20but%20also%20for%20a%20full-fledged%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20cooperation%20of%20all%20political%20parties%20is%20expected.%20I%20urge%20all%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20come%20forward%20for%20discussion%20in%20a%20cordial%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%2C%20let's%20rise%20above%20party%20lines%20to%20find%20a%20just%20and%20permanent%20solution%20for%20the%20challenges%20before%20the%20country%20in%20a%20harmonious%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20I%20wrote%20to%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20both%20houses%2C%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadhirrcinc%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40adhirrcinc%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ji%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40kharge%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ji%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20appealing%20to%20them%20for%20their%20invaluable%20cooperation%20in%20the%20discussion%20of%20the%20Manipur%20issue.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20of%20Manipur%20and...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIpGGtYSNwT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIpGGtYSNwT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Shah%20(%40AmitShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1683826545725677574%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20as%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%2C%20it%20is%20the%20collective%20duty%20of%20all%20MPs%20that%20they%20serve%20the%20interests%20of%20citizens%20and%20work%20towards%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20know%20Manipur%20is%20a%20very%20important%20border%20state%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20the%20state%20is%20the%20jewel%20of%20the%20country's%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLok%20Sabha%20has%20a%20special%20place%20in%20the%20democratic%20structure%20of%20the%20country.%20Our%20country%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%2C%20Parliament%20represents%20the%20hopes%2C%20aspirations%2C%20problems%20and%20worries%20of%20the%20140%20crore%20population%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20all%20the%20parties%20will%20cooperate%20in%20resolving%20this%20important%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20short%20debate%20on%20the%20Multi-State%20Cooperative%20Societies%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20government%20has%20nothing%20to%20hide%20and%20is%20ready%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20are%20shouting%20slogans%20are%20neither%20interested%20in%20cooperation%20nor%20in%20cooperatives%2C%20neither%20in%20Dalits%20nor%20in%20women%20welfare%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20amid%20sloganeering%20by%20opposition%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20reiterate%20that%20I%20have%20written%20letters%20to%20leaders%20of%20opposition%20in%20both%20Houses%20that%20we%20(government)%20are%20prepared%20for%20a%20discussion%20for%20as%20long%20as%20they%20want.%20The%20government%20is%20not%20afraid%20of%20anything.%20Those%20who%20want%20to%20debate%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20can%20debate.%20We%20have%20nothing%20to%20hide%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20of%20the%20country%20are%20watching%20you%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20for%20elections%2C%20beware%20of%20the%20anger%20of%20the%20people.%20I%20request%20you%20to%20create%20a%20conducive%20atmosphere%20to%20discuss%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20like%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20and%20Deputy%20Leader%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rajnath%20Singh%20too%20had%20stated%20that%20the%20government%20was%20ready%20for%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20for%20the%20second%20time%20that%20Shah%20has%20told%20the%20lower%20House%20about%20the%20government's%20willingness%20to%20hold%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20that%20Home%20Minister%20Shah%20would%20reply%20to%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProceedings%20in%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20remain%20disrupted%20ever%20since%20the%20Monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20July%2020%20with%20the%20opposition%20parties%20demanding%20a%20statement%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20before%20a%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20tried%20to%20corner%20the%20government%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20after%20a%20video%20of%20a%20May%204%20incident%20appeared%20on%20social%20media%20recently%20showing%20two%20women%20stripped%20and%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20Police%20has%20arrested%20several%20accused%20seen%20in%20the%20video.%20The%20police%20said%20a%20case%20of%20abduction%2C%20gang%20rape%20and%20murder%20has%20been%20registered%20at%20the%20Nongpok%20Sekmai%20police%20station%20in%20Thoubal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20160%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20several%20have%20been%20injured%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3