20the%20state%20government.%20What%20active%20role%20have%20you%20played%20to%20see%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20is%20implemented%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20K%20M%20Nataraj%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagaland%20has%20a%20coalition%20government%20led%20by%20the%20Nationalist%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20(NDPP)%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20outset%2C%20K%20N%20Balgopal%2C%20the%20Advocate%20General%20of%20Nagaland%2C%20submitted%20that%20the%20state%20government%20is%20keen%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20new%20law%20to%20satisfy%20the%20court%2C%20and%20sought%20time%20to%20seek%20instructions%20from%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20it%20has%20given%20numerous%20opportunities%20to%20the%20state%20government%20but%20it%20has%20done%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nataraj%20submitted%20before%20the%20court%20that%2033%25%20quota%20should%20indeed%20be%20provided%20to%20women%20in%20urban%20local%20bodies%20in%20conformity%20with%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20bench%20asked%20why%20then%20was%20it%20not%20being%20implemented%2C%20the%20ASG%20said%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20is%20not%20conducive%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGive%20us%20some%20reasonable%20time%20and%20we%20will%20have%20a%20quietus%20to%20the%20entire%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nataraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20been%20afforded%20umpteen%20opportunities%20but%20it%20has%20not%20done%20anything%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20take%20extreme%20stand%20against%20state%20governments%20which%20may%20not%20be%20amenable%20to%20you.%20Your%20own%20state%20government%20is%20violating%20the%20Constitutional%20scheme%20and%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20anything.%20How%20can%20you%20wash%20your%20hands%20of%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Colin%20Gonsalves%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%20women%20are%20willing%20to%20participate%20if%20the%20chief%20encourages%20them.%20He%20said%20participation%20of%20women%20is%20being%20obstructed%20by%20those%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20said%20in%20its%20order%2C%20%26quot%3BAdvocate%20General%20for%20Nagaland%20for%20the%20nth%20time%20seeks%20to%20assure%20the%20court%20that%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20will%20not%20be%20violated%20and%20he%20needs%20time%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20relevant%20political%20dispensation%20that%20the%20only%20way%20forward%20is%20to%20implement%20the%20constitutional%20provision...%20In%20view%20of%20the%20impassioned%20plea%20of%20the%20AG%2C%20we%20are%20inclined%20to%20give%20one%20last%20of%20the%20last%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20clarified%20that%20it%20was%20not%20interfering%20with%20the%20customary%20laws%20of%20Nagaland.%20%26quot%3BWe%20may%20only%20say%20that%20whatever%20are%20the%20customary%20laws%20of%20Nagaland%20and%20given%20the%20special%20status%20of%20the%20State%20under%20Article%20371A%2C%20are%20not%20being%20touched%20in%20any%20manner.%20This%20is%20a%20State%20where%20education%2C%20economic%20and%20social%20status%20of%20women%20is%20among%20the%20best.%20Thus%20our%20concern%20is%20why%20reservation%20for%20women%20cannot%20be%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20earlier%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20clarify%20whether%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20of%20one-third%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20municipality%20and%20town%20council%20elections%20can%20be%20violated%20by%20Nagaland%2C%20where%20the%20assembly%20had%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20repeal%20the%20municipal%20act%20and%20resolved%20not%20to%20hold%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20urban%20local%20bodies%20(ULBs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Bingenious%20method%26quot%3B%20of%20repealing%20the%20Nagaland%20Municipal%20Act%2C%202001%20was%20adopted%20to%20evade%20the%20undertaking%20given%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20about%20holding%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said%20it%20is%20an%20issue%20of%20women's%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%2C%20on%20April%205%2C%20stayed%20the%20March%2030%20notification%20cancelling%20till%20further%20orders%20the%20election%20to%20the%20ULBs%20in%20Nagaland%20which%20were%20scheduled%20for%20May%2016%20after%20almost%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20pressure%20from%20tribal%20organisations%20and%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20the%20Nagaland%20assembly%20had%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20repeal%20the%20municipal%20Act%20and%20resolved%20not%20to%20hold%20the%20elections.%20These%20organisations%20said%20Naga%20customary%20laws%20do%20not%20allow%20women%20to%20participate%20equally%20in%20the%20political%20and%20socio-economic%20decision-making%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2030%2C%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC)%20had%20issued%20a%20notification%20cancelling%20the%20election%20programme%20notified%20earlier%20%26quot%3Btill%20further%20orders%26quot%3B%20in%20view%20of%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Peoples%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20(PUCL)%20and%20others%20seeking%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20local%20bodies%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20moved%20an%20application%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20elections%20and%20urged%20it%20to%20take%20contempt%20action%20for%20%26quot%3Bdisobeying%26quot%3B%20its%20March%2014%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20seeking%20quashing%20of%20the%20March%2030%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20SEC%20cancelling%20the%20election%20schedule%2C%20the%20application%20has%20also%20sought%20setting%20aside%20of%20the%20Nagaland%20Municipal%20(Repeal)%20Act%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEC%20had%20earlier%20announced%20elections%20to%20the%2039%20ULBs%20in%20the%20state.%20Of%20the%2039%20ULBs%2C%20Kohima%2C%20Dimapur%20and%20Mokokchung%20have%20municipal%20councils%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20have%20town%20councils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Naga%20tribal%20bodies%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%20had%20opposed%20the%20ULB%20election%20under%20the%20Nagaland%20Municipal%20Act%202001%2C%20asserting%20it%20infringes%20on%20the%20special%20rights%20for%20Nagaland%20guaranteed%20by%20Article%20371-A%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202001%20Act%2C%20which%20was%20amended%20later%2C%20made%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20women%20mandatory%20for%20holding%20the%20ULB%20elections%2C%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EULB%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20have%20been%20long%20overdue%2C%20with%20the%20last%20polls%20having%20been%20held%20in%202004.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690299300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-not-willing-to-implement-constitution-supreme-court-on-quota-for-women-in-nagaland-4239475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20remarked%20today%20as%20it%20slammed%20both%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Nagaland%20government%20over%20non-implementation%20of%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20of%20one-third%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20civic%20body%20elections%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%