nial%2C%E2%80%9D%20TMC%20MP%20Sushmita%20Dev%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20took%20place%2C%20all%20parties%20attended%20and%20cooperated%20with%20him%20when%20he%20gave%20many%20assurances%20on%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20parties%20heard%20him%20but%20it%20%E2%80%9Cculminated%20in%20nothing%E2%80%9D.%20Dev%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20should%20accede%20to%20the%20point%20and%20to%20us%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20escalating%20in%20Manipur%20and%20now%20it%20is%20only%20for%20the%20PM%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20tell%20us%20what%20he%20thinks%20is%20the%20way%20forward%20and%20how%20he%20can%20explain%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20power%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Congress%20for%20a%20comment%20on%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20letter%20and%20statement.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20once%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20four%20days%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20have%20seen%20the%20opposition%20staying%20firm%20on%20its%20demand%20for%20a%20statement%20by%20Modi%20inside%20the%20House%20and%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fno-debate-yet-on-manipur-in-parliament-opposition-mps-press-for-pm-modis-statement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ediscussion%20under%20Rule%20267%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Rules%20of%20Procedures%20and%20Conduct%20of%20Business%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20only%20agreed%20to%20a%20short-term%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20127.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Mo