ment%20schemes%20and%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMinistry%20of%20Electronic%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20has%20informed%20that%20MyGov%20has%20in%20March%202023%20undertaken%20a%20process%20for%20empanelment%20of%20influencer%20marketing%20agencies%20with%20an%20objective%20of%20enabling%20wider%20dissemination%20and%20enhance%20citizen%20engagement%20in%20respect%20of%20information%20related%20to%20various%20schemes%2Fcampaigns%2Finitiatives%20of%20Government%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20the%20response%20to%20the%20bid%2C%20MyGov%20has%20empanelled%20four%20agencies.%20No%20amount%20has%20been%20spent%20under%20the%20said%20empanelment%20process%20till%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20series%20of%20interviews%20with%20Union%20ministers%20conducted%20by%20social%20media%20influencers%20in%20collaboration%20with%20MyGov%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20public%20funds%20to%20finance%20these%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3EQuestions%20Over%20Financing%20of%20Union%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Interviews%20With%20YouTube%20Influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouTube%20influencers%20like%20Ranveer%20Allahabadia%20conducted%20interviews%20with%20Union%20ministers%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Entrepreneurship%2C%20Skill%20Development%2C%20Electronics%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%3B%20Dr%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20External%20Affairs%3B%20and%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20for%20his%20YouTube%20channel%20Beer%20Biceps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20YouTube%20influencer%20Raj%20Shamani%20has%20also%20uploaded%20similar%20exclusive%20interviews%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influencers%E2%80%99%20interviews%20include%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cin%20collaboration%20with%20MyGov%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20description%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamani%20had%20also%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20interactions%20were%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntary%2C%20unpaid%20partnership%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20the%20Union%20government%20also%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuchetadalal%2Fstatus%2F1673185032884854784%5C%22%3Efront-page%20advertisements%20in%20prominent%20newspapers%3C%2Fa%3E%20endorsing%20some%20select%20social%20media%20influencers%2C%20with%20their%20images%20and%20the%20mention%20of%20their%20YouTube%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20and%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20on%20March%207%20released%20a%20tender%20inviting%20proposals%20for%20the%20empanelment%20of%20various%20Agencies%20(Social%20Media%20Marketing%20Agencies)%20handling%20Influencer%20Marketing%20or%20specialised%20Influencer%20Marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur%20told%20the%20parliament%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Communications%20(CBC)%2C%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%2C%20undertakes%20campaigns%20relating%20to%20publicity%2Fawareness%20generation%20of%20programmes%2F%20schemes%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20the%20CBC%20has%20in%20place%20transparent%20Policy%20Guidelines%20for%20empanelment%20of%20media%2Fagencies%20and%20release%20of%20advertisements%20and%20other%20promotions%20on%20media%20platforms%2C%20including%20for%20digital%20media%2Fsocial%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20use%20of%20these%20influencer%20interactions%20to%20influence%20opinions%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20shared%20a%20finance%20ministry%20order%20from%20May%20and%20accused%20the%C2%A0%20Modi%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cundermining%20the%20sanctity%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Budget%20by%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcongress-centre-usurping-publicity-funds-ministries-own-use%5C%22%3Eusurping%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2040%25%20of%20funds%20allocated%20to%20various%20ministries%20for%20publicity%20and%20handing%20it%20to%20the%20CBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690296650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F26204048%2FUnion-ministers-S.-Jaishankar-Piyush-Goyal-among-others-have-appeared-on-these-YouTube-channels-for-interviews-which-are-in-collaboration-with-MyGov.-However-there-is-opaqueness-with-regard-to-terms-of.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-money-spent-on-union-ministers-interviews-with-social-media-influencers-govt-tells-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20controversy%2C%20Union%20minister%20Anurag%20Singh%20Thakur%20said%20that%20four%20influencer%20marketing%20agencies%20have%20been%20empanelled%20for%20wider%20dissemination%20of%20government%20schemes%20and%20campaigns%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20Lok%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-money-spent-on-union-ministers-interviews-with-social-media-influencers-govt-tells-parliament%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rare%20Apple%20computer%20trainers%20on%20sale%20for%20%2450%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690296484000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk