2110608.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102110608.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3Eoppenheimer%2C%20the%20dark%20knight%2C%20interstellar%3A%20christopher%20nolan%E2%80%99s%20best%20films%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arjun%20Pereira%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fweb-stories%2Foppenheimer-the-dark-knight-interstellar-christopher-nolans-best-films%2Fphotostory%2F102110608.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20Passes%20Biological%20Diversity%20Amendment%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25193917%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-7.38.21-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2025%2C%20amid%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20loud%20protests%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20(Amendment%20Bill)%2C%202021%2C%20by%20a%20voice%20vote.%20The%20Bill%20brings%20changes%20to%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20Act%2C%202002%20by%20decriminalising%20biodiversity%20offences%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20many%20criticisms%20of%20the%20Bill%20was%20that%20it%20promotes%20%E2%80%98ease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%99%20and%20would%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20and%20Ayurveda%2C%20Yoga%20and%20Naturopathy%2C%20Unani%2C%20Siddha%2C%20and%20Homoeopathy%20(AYUSH)%20practitioners%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELok%20Sabha%20passes%20Bill%20by%20voice%20vote%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20discussed%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20(Amendment%20Bill)%2C%202021%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%2025.%20Today%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%E2%80%9D%20Bill%20is%20being%20discussed%20in%20this%20house%2C%20Yadav%20said.%20He%20added%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Significant%E2%80%99%20because%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20undergoing%20a%20triple%20crisis%20now.%20On%20one%20side%20is%20the%20crisis%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20on%20another%20is%20the%20crisis%20of%20desertification%20of%20land%2C%20and%20on%20the%20third%2C%20the%20crisis%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20biological%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20country%2C%20we%20want%20to%20promote%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%A6by%20%5Bdecriminalising%20offences%5D%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20and%20ease%20of%20living%20is%20being%20brought%20forward%20by%20this%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20spoke%20right%20through%20loud%20protests%20%E2%80%93%20by%20the%20opposition%20pertaining%20to%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20background.%20The%20Bill%20was%20passed%20by%20voice%20vote%20later%20and%20the%20House%20adjourned%20till%205%20pm%20immediately%20after%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Biological%20Diversity%20Amendment%20Bill%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20will%20amend%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20Act%2C%202002%2C%20which%20provides%20for%20the%20conservation%20of%20biological%20diversity%20in%20India%20and%20their%20sustainable%20use%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fair%20and%20equitable%20sharing%20of%20the%20benefits%20that%20arise%20from%20using%20biodiversity.%20It%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2016%2C%202021%2C%20by%20Yadav.%20Experts%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbiodiversity-amendments-further-isolate-agriculture-environment-ministries%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eargued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Bill%20encourages%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20investments%20%E2%80%93%20promotes%20%E2%80%9Cease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20simplifies%20the%20patent%20application%20process%2C%20and%20that%20it%20will%20further%20alienate%20India%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20and%20environment%20ministries.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20concern%20that%20the%20Bill%20will%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20and%20AYUSH%20practitioners%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%2C%20following%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvidhilegalpolicy.in%2Fresearch%2Fcomments-to-the-joint-committee-on-parliament-on-the-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-2021%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriticisms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20chaired%20by%20Sanjay%20Jaiswal.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20was%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20on%20August%202%2C%202022.%20Some%20experts%20have%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20has%20addressed%20several%20points%20raised%20by%20critics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOur%20major%20submission%20was%20reg.%20the%20ambiguous%20definition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20controlled%20company%E2%80%9D%20which%20would%20have%20changed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%20altogether.%20Glad%20that%20the%20report%20not%20just%20discusses%20this%20point%20but%20accepting%20our%20suggestion%20of%20S2(27)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FR8t42n0Wvj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FR8t42n0Wvj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Debadityo%20Sinha%20(%40debadityo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdebadityo%2Fstatus%2F1554507332603691008%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%202%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20committee%20accepted%20several%20amendments%20%E2%80%93%20including%20ones%20that%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiological-diversity-bill-passed-amid-opposition-protests-on-manipur-violence-101690279400291.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20experts%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvidhilegalpolicy.in%2Fresearch%2Fcomments-to-the-joint-committee-on-parliament-on-the-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-2021%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20concerns%20about%20the%20Bill%20decriminalising%20offences%20under%20the%20Act%20and%20making%20them%20punishable%20only%20with%20a%20penalty%20(between%20Rs%201%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20and%20continuing%20violations%20can%20attract%20an%20additional%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore)%20and%20no%20imprisonment.%20The%20committee%20merely%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbilltrack%2Fprs-products%2Fjpc-report-summary%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Bill%2520was%2520introduced%2520in%2Cassociated%2520knowledge%2520with%2520local%2520communities.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20penalty%20structure%20should%20not%20be%20too%20meagre%20as%20it%20could%20enable%20violators%20to%20escape%20with%20a%20small%20fine.%20It%20recommended%20that%20the%20penalty%20should%20be%20proportionate%20to%20the%20gains%20obtained%20by%20entities%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690294840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25193917%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-7.38.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bill%20was%20cleared%20amidst%20loud%20protests%20by%20the%20opposition%20regarding%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Don't%20Know%20How%20It...%5C%22%3A%20Kapil%20Dev%20On%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20team's%20Chances%20At%20WC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20enter%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%20as%20obvious%20favourites%2C%20and%20former%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kapil%20Dev%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40958-ramlal-nikhanj-kapil-dev-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20the%20home%20side%20should%20tame%20the%20pressure%20of%20expectations%20to%20regain%20the%20trophy.%20Two-time%20champions%20India%20will%20be%20keen%20to%20add%20another%20title%20to%20their%20cabinet%20after%20a%20hiatus%20of%2012%20years%20during%20the%20October%205-November%2019%20tournament.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20it%20will%20pan%20out.%20They%20are%20yet%20to%20announce%20the%20team%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20India%20will%20always%20enter%20a%20tournament%20as%20favourites%20as%20it%20has%20been%20the%20case%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kapil%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20launch%20of%20Golf%20Fitting%20Centre%20here%20at%20the%20Karnataka%20Golf%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20how%20the%20team%20comes%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20expectations%20from%20all%20sides.%20We%20have%20won%20a%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20team%2C%20whoever%20gets%20selected%2C%20can%20do%20it%20again.%20A%20World%20Cup%20is%20coming%20in%20four%20years%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20the%20players%20will%20be%20fully%20prepared%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kapil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20career%20in%20which%20he%20played%20131%20Tests%20and%20225%20ODIs%2C%20Kapil%20never%20really%20had%20to%20take%20a%20break%20owing%20to%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20modern%20times%2C%20injury%20breakdowns%20of%20cricketers%20have%20become%20more%20frequent%20despite%20fresh%20fitness%20concepts%20coming%20in%20vogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20pace%20spearhead%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20out%20of%20action%20for%20nearly%20a%20year%20now%2C%20and%20his%20return%20is%20still%20largely%20a%20matter%20of%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20said%20workload%20and%20injury%20management%20should%20be%20given%20due%20care%20considering%20the%20amount%20of%20cricket%20the%20players%20are%20involved%20in%20this%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20time%20was%20different%20as%20we%20hardly%20played%20so%20much%20cricket.%20Now%2C%20these%20players%20are%20playing%20some%2010%20months%20of%20cricket.%20So%2C%20managing%20your%20body%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20away%20from%20injuries.%20Everybody's%20body%20is%20different%20and%20they%20would%20require%20individual%20plans%20to%20preserve%20their%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kapil%2C%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%20winning%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20belongs%20to%20that%20generation%20of%20cricketers%20who%20have%20prided%20themselves%20in%20giving%20their%20best%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%2C