vil%20society%20groups%20over%20their%20demand%20for%20making%20Tura%20the%20winter%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20after%20the%20attack%20that%20left%2018%20security%20personnel%20injured%2C%20Mr%20Sangma%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20civil%20society%20groups%20had%20expressed%20surprise%20as%20the%20people%20who%20started%20the%20attack%20did%20not%20belong%20to%20their%20organisations.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20indication%20that%20the%20mob%20came%20from%20outside%2C%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20civil%20society%20leaders%20were%20peacefully%20discussing%20the%20winter%20capital%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20chief%20said%20money%20and%20liquor%20had%20been%20distributed%20on%20July%2023%20near%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20office%2C%20where%20the%20meeting%20was%20taking%20place%2C%20to%20create%20trouble%20and%20spark%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mob%20attacked%20the%20CMO%20(chief%20minister's%20office)%20in%20Tura%20when%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20having%20a%20meeting%20with%2018%20representatives%20from%20NGOs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20meeting%20started%20at%203.15%20pm%20and%20continued%20till%205.45%20pm.%20It%20was%20a%20long%20meeting%20where%20the%20discussions%20basically%20concentrated%20on%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20NGOs.%20There%20were%20two%20demands%2C%20specifically%20the%20first%20was%20on%20making%20Tura%20the%20winter%20capital%20of%20Meghalaya%2C%20and%20the%20other%20was%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20reservation%20policy%20or%20roster%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bishnoi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20NGOs%20were%20discussing%20in%20a%20peaceful%20atmosphere%20when%20suddenly%20the%20crowd%20started%20raising%20slogans%2C%20following%20which%20the%20NGO%20leaders%20were%20sent%20outside%20to%20calm%20them%20down%2C%20but%20they%20turned%20violent%20and%20started%20throwing%20stones%20on%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20leaders%20also%20told%20Mr%20Sangma%20that%20they%20saw%20some%20people%20in%20the%20crowd%20who%20were%20not%20part%20of%20any%20discussion%20or%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20to%20lathi-charge%20the%20mob%2C%20which%20dispersed%20after%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bishnoi%20said%20the%20mob%20threw%20stones%2C%20damaged%2021%20vehicles%2C%20of%20which%20they%20set%20four%20on%20fire.%20Eighteen%20people%20were%20injured%20-%2010%20from%20Meghalaya%20Police%2C%20one%20Home%20Guard%20and%20seven%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690294140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhjmrtdhc_conrad-1200_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-attack-on-meghalaya-chief-minister-office-was-planned-top-cop-4239314%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20night's%20mob%20attack%20at%20the%20office%20of%20Meghalaya%20Chief%20Minister%20Conrad%20Sangma%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20planned%20well%20in%20advance%2C%20the%20police%20chief%20of%20the%20northeast%20state%20told%20reporters%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-attack-on-meghalaya-chief-minister-office-was-planned-top-cop-4239314%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-attack-on-meghalaya-chief-minister-office-was-planned-top-cop-4239314%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-attack-on-meghalaya-chief-minister-office-was-planned-top-cop-4239314%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Never%20Too%20Late%3A%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20Must%20Decide%20What%20Kind%20of%20President%20She%20Wishes%20To%20Be%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20