blemakers-unravelling-the-role-of-manipurs-meira-paibis-or-meitei-moms%2F1680754%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20gather%20in%20places%20to%20block%20the%20security%20forces%20based%20on%20leads%20from%20the%20state%20police%2C%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines%20now%2C%20who%20must%20be%20kept%20informed%20of%20operations%20and%20their%20movements%20by%20the%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20current%20rules%20of%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foot%20soldiers%20of%20Meitei%20nationalism%2C%20who%20have%20been%20at%20the%20frontline%20and%20were%20present%20on%20that%20fateful%20day%20in%20the%20village%20that%20was%20looted%20with%20%E2%80%9Csophisticated%20weapons%E2%80%9D%2C%20are%20even%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR.%20They%20were%20members%20of%20Meitei%20Leepun%20(whose%20founder%20openly%20expressed%20his%20loyalty%20to%20Singh%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDJnPewUhmU%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%253DVDJnPewUhmU%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1690355034036000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3HYI3Sb1FM2_-CFxhNUg-M%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Karan%20Thapar)%2C%20Kangleipak%20Kunba%20Lup%2C%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Meitei%20Council.%20They%20share%20much%20of%20their%20ideology%20with%20banned%20secessionist%20groups%20like%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%20and%20Kanglei%20Yawol%20Kunna%20Lup%20(KYKL)%2C%20who%20had%20killed%2019%20Indian%20Army%20personnel%20in%20a%202017%20ambush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20groups%20ever%20entered%20into%20formal%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20remaining%20true%20to%20their%20cause.%20With%20no%20desire%20to%20secede%20from%20India%2C%20these%20armed%20radical%20groups%20are%20a%20more%20acceptable%20version%20of%20the%20Meitei%20n