%20Support%20Personnel%2C%20relating%20to%20%26quot%3Bshowing%20dissent%20at%20an%20umpire's%20decision%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaur%20was%20also%20fined%2025%20percent%20of%20her%20match%20fee%20for%20a%20Level%201%20offence%20relating%20to%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20criticism%20in%20relation%20to%20an%20incident%20occurring%20in%20an%20international%20match%26quot%3B%20when%2C%20during%20the%20presentation%20ceremony%2C%20Kaur%20openly%20criticised%20the%20umpiring%20in%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20said%20in%20its%20release%20that%20Harmanpreet%20admitted%20to%20the%20offences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20captain%20admitted%20the%20offences%20and%20agreed%20to%20the%20sanctions%20proposed%20by%20Akhtar%20Ahmed%20of%20the%20Emirates%20ICC%20International%20Panel%20of%20Match%20Referees.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20a%20formal%20hearing%2C%20and%20the%20penalties%20were%20implemented%20promptly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICC%20said..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Level%202%20breach%20typically%20carries%20a%20penalty%20ranging%20from%2050%20to%20100%20percent%20of%20the%20player's%20match%20fee%2C%20and%20three%20or%20four%20demerit%20points%2C%20while%20a%20Level%201%20breach%20entails%20a%20minimum%20penalty%20of%20an%20official%20reprimand%2C%20up%20to%20a%20maximum%20penalty%20of%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20player's%20match%20fee%2C%20and%20one%20or%20two%20demerit%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kaur's%20instance%2C%20the%20accumulation%20of%20four%20demerit%20points%20converted%20to%20two%20suspension%20points%2C%20leading%20to%20her%20suspension%20from%20either%20one%20Test%20match%20or%20two%20ODIs%20or%20two%20T20Is%2C%20whichever%20comes%20first%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690291920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fmbl7cf3_harmanpreet-kaur_625x300_22_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv