t%20out.%20In%20the%20near%20term%2C%20I%20have%20some%20pressing%20family%20issues%20that%20need%20my%20fuller%20attention%20so%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Zen%20proverb%20that%20the%20tea%20cup%20must%20be%20empty%20before%20it%20can%20be%20full%2C%20I%20will%20take%20August%20off%20and%20then%20spend%20September%20looking%20after%20my%20mum%20in%20India%20and%20only%20start%20thinking%20about%20work%20in%20October%20with%20a%20view%20to%20doing%20more%20things%20in%202024%2C''%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20the%20full%20post%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7088127255960240128%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20Mr.%20Chinnappa%20did%20his%20BA%20in%20Economics%20and%20Policy%20Studies%20from%20Rice%20University%20and%20his%20schooling%20from%20Jakarta%20International%20School.%20Prior%20to%20Google%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20BBC%2C%20United%20Business%20Media%20(UBM)%2C%20and%20Associated%20Press%20Television%20News%20(APTN).%C2%A0He%20has%2029%20years%20of%20professional%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgoogle-parent-company-alphabet-to-lay-off-12-000-globally-report-3709708%5C%22%3E12%2C000%20people%20were%20affected%20worldwide%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20the%20mass%20layoffs%20that%20Google%20announced%20in%20January%20this%20year.%C2%A0Alphabet%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20told%20staff%20in%20a%20memo%20that%20the%20firm%20had%20reviewed%20its%20products%2C%20people%2C%20and%20priorities%2C%20leading%20to%20job%20cuts%20across%20geographies%20and%20tech.%20He%20said%20the%20layoffs%20were%20necessitated%20by%20the%20economic%20downturn%20and%20required%20for%20the%20long-term%20health%20of%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20these%20changes%20will%20impact%20the%20lives%20of%20Googlers%20weighs%20heavily%20on%20me%2C%20and%20I%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20decisions%20that%20led%20us%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Pichai%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20cuts%C2%A0were%20made%20after%20careful%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690289880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fc59a2s6o_madhav-chinnappa_625x300_25_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogles-indian-origin-director-of-news-laid-off-after-13-years-in-the-end-4239275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Notably%2C%20Madhav%20Chinnappa%20joined%20Google%20in%202010%20as%20the%20head%20of%20strategic%20partnerships%20at%20Google%20News.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogles-indian-origin-director-of-news-laid-off-after-13-years-in-the-end-4239275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogles-indian-origin-director-of-news-laid-off-after-13-years-in-the-end-4239275%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogles-indian-origin-director-of-news-laid-off-after-13-years-in-the-end-4239275%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Replaces%20Qin%20Gang%20as%20Foreign%20Minister%20a%20Month%20After%20He%20Was%20Last%20Seen%20in%20Public%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25181139%2FQin_Gang_and_Wang_Yi_2023.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20month%20after%20he%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20public%2C%20Qin%20Gang%20has%20been%20removed%20as%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Chinese%20state%20news%20agency%20X