anual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20(PEMSR)%20Act%2C%202013.%20The%20Act%20bans%20the%20use%20of%20any%20individual%20for%20manually%20cleaning%2C%20carrying%2C%20disposing%20of%2C%20or%20otherwise%20handling%2C%20in%20any%20manner%2C%20human%20excreta%20till%20its%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20question%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20Self-Employment%20Scheme%20of%20Liberation%20%26amp%3B%20Rehabilitation%20of%20Scavengers%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20budget%202023-24%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20scheme%20has%20been%20renamed%20as%20National%20Action%20for%20Mechanised%20Sanitation%20Ecosystem%20(NAMASTE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmanual-scavengers-rehabilitation-scheme-progress-report%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20March%202022%2C%20researchers%20Jawed%20Alam%20Khan%20and%20Rahat%20Tasneem%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20obstinate%20denial%20regarding%20the%20existence%20of%20manual%20scavenging%20is%20proving%20to%20be%20detrimental%20in%20making%20any%20real%20progress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Self-Employment%20Scheme%20of%20Liberation%20%26amp%3B%20Rehabilitation%20of%20Scavengers%20(SRMS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20government%20interventions%20for%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20practice.%20Implemented%20by%20the%20National%20Safai%20Karmacharis%20Finance%20and%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSKFDC)%20more%20than%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20is%20far%20from%20meeting%20its%20goals.%20Launched%20in%202007%2C%20the%20objective%20of%20SRMS%20was%20to%20rehabilitate%20manual%20scavengers%20and%20their%20dependents%20in%20alternative%20occupations%20by%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690288727000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F06191314%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-06-at-7.12.59-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F339-lives-lost-to-manual-scavenging-in-the-last-five-years-govt-data-reveals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20manual%20scavenging%20is%20an%20outlawed%20practice%20under%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20(PEMSR)%20Act%2C%202013%2C%20several%20die%20every%20year%20cleaning%20sewers%20and%20septic%20tanks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F339-lives-lost-to-manual-scavenging-in-the-last-five-years-govt-data-reveals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actors%20who%20have%20been%20part%20of%20music%20videos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690287900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102108582%2Cimgsize-67470.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Factors-who-have-been-part-of-music-videos%2Fphotostory%2F102108582.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102108582.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Factors-who-have-been-part-of-music-videos%2Fphotostory%2F102108582.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajakumari%20gives%20a%20glimpse%20of%20her%20Jawan%20rap%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690287338000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102110339%2Cimgsize-31972.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frajakumari-gives-a-glimpse-of-her-rap-from-shah-rukh-khans-jawan%2Farticlesh