20Ranveer%20Singh%20and%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20to%20shoot%20a%20special%20sequence%20for%20the%20film.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famidst-reports-of-vicky-kaushal-opting-out-of-singham-again-rohit-shetty-shares-update-on-the-starcast%2Farticleshow%2F102110428.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ABVP%20Members%20'Attack'%20Gorakhpur%20University%20VC%2C%20Registrar%3B%20FIR%20Registered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25171744%2Funiversity-4-.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGorakhpur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Akhil%20Bhartiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%20members%2C%20who%20claim%20to%20follow%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20motto%20of%20%E2%80%98Knowledge%2C%20Modesty%20and%20Unity%E2%80%99%2C%20allegedly%20beat%20up%20the%20registrar%20of%20Gorakhpur%20University%2C%20Professor%20Ajay%20Singh%2C%20and%20pushed%20and%20shoved%20the%20vice-chancellor%2C%20Professor%20Rajesh%20Singh%2C%20on%20Friday%20(July%2021)%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VC%E2%80%99s%20office%20was%20ransacked%20and%20a%20flower%20pot%20was%20hurled%20at%20his%20car.%20The%20alleged%20ABVP%20members%20also%20attacked%20police%20personnel%20who%20were%20trying%20to%20escort%20the%20VC%20out%20of%20the%20campus.%20Later%20the%20police%20lathi-charged%20and%20arrested%20eight%20members.%20To%20get%20the%20arrested%20persons%20released%2C%20other%20ABVP%20members%20then%20blocked%20the%20road%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Cantt%20police%20station%2C%20which%20ended%20in%20the%20police%20resorting%20to%20lathi%20charge%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20complaint%20of%20university%20proctor%20Satyapal%20Singh%2C%20the%20Cantt%20Police%20registered%20an%20FIR%20under%20IPC%20Sections%20147%2C%20342%2C%20427%20and%20323%20against%20eight%20students%20of%20the%20university%2C%20one%20contractor%20and%2013%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruckus%20erupted%20in%20the%20administrative%20block%20of%20Gorakhpur%20University%20when%20the%20VC%20refused%20to%20meet%20ABVP%20members%20who%20were%20protesting%20on%20several%20issues%2C%20including%20a%20fee%20hike%2C%20and%20began%20to%20leave%20his%20office.%20The%20ABVP%20members%20then%20attacked%20Rajesh%2C%20although%20he%20was%20being%20escorted%20by%20the%20police.%20While%20the%20police%20and%20university%20guards%20somehow%20managed%20to%20shield%20him%2C%20the%20officiating%20registrar%20Ajay%20was%20surrounded%20by%20ABVP%20members.%20A%20video%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20shows%20several%20young%20men%20with%20saffron%20%3Cem%3Egamchhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20around%20their%20necks%20push%20him%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20kick%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20have%20gone%20viral.%20One%20of%20the%20videos%20shows%20ABVP%20members%20trying%20to%20pull%20Rajesh%20by%20his%20waist.%20During%20the%20tussle%2C%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20slap%20him%20and%20he%20barely%20resisted%20being%20pushed%20down.%20Two%20policemen%20who%20tried%20to%20rescue%20him%20also%20fell%20prey%20to%20the%20attackers.%20One%20policeman%20was%20thrashed%2C%20his%20badge%20was%20snatched%20and%20his%20cap%20was%20pulled.%20Another%20policeman%20was%20pushed%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20beaten%20up.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20police%20personnel%20also%20hit%20ABVP%20protesters%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20July%2013%2C%20the%20proctor%20had%20also%20been%20assaulted%20by%20alleged%20ABVP%20members%20who%20were%20burning%20an%20effigy%20of%20the%20VC%20at%20the%20university%20gate.%20He%20gave%20a%20statement%20in%20the%20Cantt%20police%20station%2C%20but%20the%20police%20neither%20registered%20an%20FIR%20nor%20took%20any%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20administration%20had%20suspended%20four%20students%20and%20barred%20the%20entry%20of%20four%20outsiders%20for%20assaulting%20the%20proctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EABVP%20members%20carried%20out%20a%20demonstration%20on%20June%2026%20and%20presented%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20VC%20regarding%20the%20fee%20hike%2C%20demanding%20proper%20hostel%20arrangements%2C%20student%20union%20elections%2C%20arrangements%20for%20provision%20of%20degrees%20in%20ten%20days%2C%20timely%20declaration%20of%20exam%20results%2C%20ensuring%20admission%20of%20EWS%20candidates%20in%20research%20entrance%20examination%20in%20the%20Hindi%20department%20and%20seeking%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20recruitment%20of%20assistant%20professors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20began%20at%20the%20administrative%20office%20on%20July%2018%20regarding%20the%20fee%20hike%20and%20lifting%20of%20suspension%20orders%20of%20ABVP%20members.%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20the%20dharna%2C%20there%20was%20a%20ruckus%20over%20the%20vice-chancellor%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20meet%20the%20protestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ABVP%20has%20denied%20any%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20VC%20and%20registrar%20and%20vandalism%20of%20their%20offices%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20miscreants%20who%20attacked%20the%20registrar%20and%20university%20guards%20and%20threw%20pots%20at%20the%20VC%E2%80%99s%20car.%20ABVP%E2%80%99s%20organising%20secretary%20Haridev%20alleged%20that%20the%20VC%20asked%20the%20police%20to%20lathicharge%20the%20members%20and%20eight%20of%20them%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20media%20and%20public%20relations%20office%20about%20the%20incident%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20miscreants%20who%20forcefully%20entered%20the%20vice-chancellor%E2%80%99s%20office%20located%20in%20the%20administrative%20building%20and%20assaulted%20the%20officials.%20The%20students%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%20have%20been%20expelled%20from%20the%20university%20with%20immediate%20effect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CInvolvement%20of%20some%20contractors%20has%20also%20been%20reported%20who%20financed%20the%20entire%20incident.%20These%20contractors%20have%20been%20blacklisted%20from%20the%20university%20and%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20them.%20Their%20entry%20on%20the%20university%20campus%20has%20also%20been%20banned.%20Some%20teachers%20were%20also%20found%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20incident.%20Action%20is%20being%20taken%20against%20them%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%20given%20to%20the%20police%2C%20at%20around%2011%20am%20on%20July%2021%20some%20people%2C%20including%20some%20students%2C%20forcefully%20entered%20the%20administrative%20building%20of%20the%20university.%20They%20started%20creating%20a%20ruckus%20on%20campus%20by%20vandalising%20equipment%2C%20flower%20pots%2C%20mirror%2C%20chairs%20and%20other%20things%20in%20the%20VC%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20car.%20The%20university%20officials%20including%20the%20VC%2C%20finance%20officer%2C%20registrar%2C%20controller%20and%20others%20were%20locked%20in%20their%20cells.%20Some%20external%20elements%20were%20also%20encouraging%20the%20unruly%20students%20to%20action.%20The%20attackers%20deliberately%20obstructed%20official%20work%20of%20the%20university%20staff%2C%20which%20forced%20them%20to%20call%20the%20police%20for%20security.%20However%2C%20they%20continued%20to%20create%20a%20nuisance%20even%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20police%20and%20refused%20to%20calm%20down%20even%20when%20the%20police%20tried%20to%20convince%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20continues%20that%20the%20VC%20was%20somehow%20escorted%20out%20under%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20police%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20impending%20threat%20to%20him.%20Other%20university%20officials%20also%20managed%20to%20escape%20when%20they%20got%20the%20opportunity.%20But%20the%20registrar%20fell%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20miscreants%20and%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20pacify%20them%2C%20the%20miscreants%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20familiar%20to%20him%2C%20launched%20an%20attack%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20killing%20him.%20He%20was%20slapped%2C%20punched%20and%20hit%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head%20with%20a%20blunt%20object%2C%20which%20caused%20injury%20and%20blood%20loss.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20fell%20on%20the%20ground%20but%20the%20miscreants%20continued%20to%20attack%20him%20and%20he%20received%20injuries%20on%20his%20whole%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20some%20intervention%2C%20he%20was%20rescued%20from%20the%20attackers%20but%20by%20then%20he%20had%20suffered%20grave%20injuries.%20The%20registrar%20has%20recently%20undergone%20coronary%20angioplasty%20for%20stent%20placement.%20There%20was%20every%20possibility%20that%20the%20attack%20by%20the%20unruly%20elements%20could%20have%20cost%20the%20registrar%20his%20life.%20The%20entire%20incident%20was%20captured%20on%20the%20CCTV%20camera%20installed%20near%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20proctor%2C%20Satyapal%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20attacked%20on%20July%2013%20for%20stopping%20miscreants%20from%20burning%20an%20effigy%20of%20the%20VC%20at%20the%20university%20gate.%20He%20said%20he%20even%20gave%20a%20statement%20but%20the%20Cantt%20Police%20did%20not%20register%20an%20FIR.%20No%20preventive%20or%20any%20other%20action%20was%20taken%2C%20which%20emboldened%20the%20unruly%20elements%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20fresh%20attack%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20contractor%20Piyush%20Singh%20is%20the%20main%20conspirator%20in%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20registrar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaridev%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20activists%20of%20ABVP%E2%80%99s%20Gorakhpur%20University%20unit%20were%20protesting%20peacefully%20for%20the%20last%20four%20days%20against%20the%20irregularities%20prevailing%20in%20the%20university%20and%20the%20orders%20related%20to%20suspension%20and%20ban%20on%20entry%20of%20ABVP%20workers.%20But%20the%20VC%20refused%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20protesting%20students%20and%20began%20to%20leave%20his%20office%20accompanied%20by%20heavy%20police%20force.%20When%20the%20ABVP%20protesters%20requested%20to%20talk%20to%20him%20again%2C%20CO%20Yogendra%20Singh%20and%20university%20chowki%20in-charge%20Amit%20Chaudhary%20began%20lathi-charging%20them.%20Police%20presence%20emboldened%20VC%20Prof%20Rajesh%20Singh%20and%20he%20resorted%20to%20lathicharge.%20They%20even%20misbehaved%20with%20female%20activists.%20One%20activist%20Deepak%20Pandey%20was%20seriously%20injured%20and%20many%20others%20have%20also%20suffered%20injuries.%20ABVP%20activists%20Mayank%20Rai%2C%20Rishabh%20Singh%2C%20Arpit%20Kasaudhan%2C%20Prince%20Tiwari%2C%20Shakti%20Singh%2C%20Shivam%20Pandey%2C%20Shubham%20Rao%20and%20Alok%20Gupta%20were%20taken%20to%20Cantt%20police%20station%20by%20the%20police.%20ABVP%20condemns%20such%20gruesome%20handling%20of%20the%20students%2C%20and%20if%20the%20activists%20are%20not%20released%2C%20ABVP%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20carry%20out%20violent%20agitation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVC%20Rajesh%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-year%20term%20of%20this%20VC%20ends%20on%20September%205.%20The%20process%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20a%20new%20VC%20has%20already%20been%20initiated%20by%20the%20chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20has%20run%20into%20controversies%20several%20times%20during%20his%20tenure.%20He%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20acting%20arbitrarily%20in%20defiance%20of%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20statutes%2C%20starting%20more%20than%20five%20dozen%20courses%20without%20proper%20approval%20from%20the%20state%20government%20and%20making%20necessary%20arrangements%2C%20harassing%20teachers%20and%20being%20involved%20in%20financial%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindi%20department%20Professor%20Kamlesh%20Gupta%20was%20suspended%20twice%20for%20questioning%20the%20VC.%20His%20suspension%20order%20was%20withdrawn%20after%20the%20high%20court%20stayed%20it%2C%20but%20a%20few%20days%20later%20he%20was%20suspended%20again.%20Gupta%20carried%20out%20a%20protest%2C%20and%20seven%20professors%20who%20supported%20his%20protest%20were%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices%20and%20lost%20one%20day%E2%80%99s%20salary.%20When%20chaos%20erupted%20in%20the%20university%2C%20the%20OSD%20to%20the%20chancellor%20immediately%20reached%20Gorakhpur%20to%20handle%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VC%20allowed%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20Department%20of%20Physical%20Education%2C%20Institute%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Technology%20and%20Institute%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Natural%20Sciences%20without%20a%20proper%20building%2C%20teaching%20faculty%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20accepted%20admissions%20for%2067%20new%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202021%2C%20Rajesh%20had%20removed%20the%20then%20registrar%2C%20Omprakash%2C%20from%20his%20post%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20non-cooperation%2C%20and%20made%20Ajay%20the%20officiating%20registrar.%20Omprakash%20stood%20his%20ground%20and%20challenged%20the%20VC%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20claiming%20that%20according%20to%20the%20University%20Act%2C%20the%20VC%20did%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20remove%20him%20from%20the%20post.%20Later%2C%20the%20state%20government%20also%20intervened%20and%20said%20that%20the%20VC%20cannot%20remove%20the%20registrar.%20The%20dispute%20ended%20with%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20registrar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20VC%20had%20another%20confrontation%20with%20the%20president%20of%20the%20University%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%2C%20Professor%20Vinod%20Singh%2C%20following%20which%20the%20latter%20resigned%20from%20the%20post.%20Since%20then%2C%20teachers%E2%80%99%20union%20elections%20have%20not%20been%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20has%20also%20had%20several%20confrontations%20with%20the%20office%20bearers%20of%20the%20College%20Teachers%20Association%20(GUACTA)%20affiliated%20to%20Gorakhpur%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20of%20the%20university%20have%20been%20agitating%20to%20demand%20student%20union%20elections%20and%20examinations%20for%20about%201%2C000%20pre-PhD%20students%20under%20the%20new%20system%2C%20as%20well%20as%20against%20poor%20conditions%20of%20hostels%2C%20the%20fee%20hike%20and%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20proctor%20Professor%20Gopal%20Prasad%20had%20resigned%2C%20accusing%20the%20VC%20of%20behaving%20indecently%20and%20pressurising%20him%20to%20do%20inappropriate%20things.%20The%20VC%20is%20also%20accused%20of%20caste%20bias%20and%20of%20favouring%20a%20few%20teachers%20and%20handing%20them%20most%20university%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rajesh%20has%20always%20remained%20unperturbed%20by%20these%20allegations.%20He%20cites%20getting%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20A%2B%2B%20accreditation%20in%20the%20NAAC%20and%20starting%2067%20new%20courses%20as%20his%20major%20achievements.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20he%20has%20often%20tried%20hard%20to%20prove%20his%20closeness%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20many%20have%20been%20wondering%20about%20the%20real%20reason%20behind%20the%20attack%20on%20him%20by%20the%20workers%20of%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20subsidiary%20student%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Hindi%20original%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690286745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25171744%2Funiversity-4-.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fabvp-members-attack-gorakhpur-university-vc-registrar-fir-registered%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20members%20of%20the%20ABVP%20have%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%2C%20leading%20to%20further%20protests%20by%20the%20organisation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fabvp-members-attack-gorakhpur-university-vc-registrar-fir-registered%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Narendra%20Modi%20is%20Vishwaguru%20to%20'Spin%20Dictators'%20the%20World%20Over%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23153053%2FUntitled-design-7-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CForty-seven%20years%20ago%20on%20June%2026%2C%20democracy%20was%20made%20a%20hostage%2C%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20crush%20democracy%20which%20is%20our%20pride%20and%20in%20the%20DNA%20of%20every%20Indian%E2%80%A6The%20courts%2C%20every%20constitutional%20institution%2C%20and%20the%20press%20were%20put%20under%20control%E2%80%A6Thousands%20were%20arrested%20and%20lakhs%20suffered%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpeople-lost-even-right-to-life-during-emergency-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F92478174.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20June%2026%20last%20year%2C%20speaking%20eloquently%20about%20the%20assault%20on%20democratic%20rights%20during%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20the%20striking%20similarities.%20During%20his%20nine-year%20rule%2C%20Modi%20has%20outdone%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%20every%20kind%20of%20democratic%20transgression.%20Under%20him%2C%20rights%20have%20been%20taken%20away%20without%20invoking%20Article%20352%20(proclamation%20of%20emergency)%2C%20the%20media%20has%20been%20tamed%20sans%20formal%20censorship%2C%20watchdog%20bodies%20have%20become%20toothless%2C%20and%20political%20prisoners%20have%20been%20left%20to%20languish%20under%20draconian%20laws%20that%20make%20the%20grant%20of%20bail%20difficult%20if%20not%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchristophe-jaffrelot-indira-gandhi-emergency-bjp%5C%22%3EInterview%3A%20%E2%80%98Many%20Differences%20but%20Also%20Similarities%20Between%20Now%20and%20Emergency%20in%201975%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20admirers%20hail%20all%20of%20this%20as%20%E2%80%98Modi%20magic%E2%80%99%2C%20his%20critics%20attribute%20them%20to%20the%20teflon%20around%20him%20which%20allows%20him%20to%20retain%20dictatorial%20control%20over%20the%20system.%20But%20a%20new%20book%20%3Cem%3ESpin%20Dictators%20%E2%80%94%20The%20Changing%20Face%20of%20Tyranny%20in%20the%2021st%20Century%3C%2Fem%3E%20offers%20us%20a%20different%20explanation.%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20that%20the%20much-hailed%20Modi%20halo%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20phenomenon%2C%20but%20that%20he%20has%20only%20followed%20the%2021st%20century%20dictators%E2%80%99%20standard%20playbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20334px)%2085vw%2C%20334px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25183101%2F0691211418.01._SCLZZZZZZZ_SX500_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22334%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25183101%2F0691211418.01._SCLZZZZZZZ_SX500_.jpg%20329w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25183101%2F0691211418.01._SCLZZZZZZZ_SX500_-197x300.jpg%20197w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665051%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22508%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDaniel%20Treisman%20and%20Sergei%20Guriev%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3ESpin%20Dictators%3A%20The%20Changing%20Face%20of%20Tyranny%20in%20the%2021st%20Century%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EPrinceton%20University%20Press%20(April%202022)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%20by%20Sergei%20Guriev%20and%20Daniel%20Treisman%2C%20%3Cem%3ESpin%20Dictators%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20in%20the%20genre%20of%20the%202018%20book%20%3Cem%3EHow%20Democracies%20Die%20%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20political%20scientists%20Steven%20Levitsky%20and%20Daniel%20Ziblatt.%20Guriev%20and%20Treisman%20divide%20dictators%20into%20two%20categories%3A%20fear%20and%20spin.%20While%20conventional%20dictators%20retained%20power%20by%20resorting%20to%20violent%20and%20oppressive%20means%2C%20the%2021st%20century%20has%20produced%20a%20new%20smart%20set%20whom%20the%20authors%20aptly%20call%20%E2%80%98spin%20dictators%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20dictators%20who%20ruled%20by%20fear%2C%20the%20new%20crop%20of%20dictators%20avoid%20violent%20methods%20like%20repressing%20and%20punishing%20opposition%2C%20suspension%20of%20rights%2C%20resorting%20to%20mass%20arrests%2C%20outright%20media%20censorship%2C%20blocking%20cross-border%20communication%2C%20and%20holding%20fake%20elections%20in%20which%20the%20boss%20wins%20with%2099%25%20votes.%20The%20spin%20dictators%20won%E2%80%99t%20physically%20terrorise%20their%20political%20opposition%20but%20will%20doggedly%20prosecute%20them%20for%20tax%20violations%20and%20libel.%20Outright%20political%20murders%20are%20rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModern%20dictators%20%E2%80%93%20including%20our%20own%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20manipulate%20the%20information%20flow%20to%20shape%20public%20opinion%20and%20thus%20create%20public%20support%20in%20their%20favour.%20Their%20strategy%20is%20to%20transform%2C%20adapt%2C%20and%20exploit%20the%20weak%20spots%20in%20democracy%20for%20their%20own%20sustenance%20in%20the%20changing%20environment.%20They%20invest%20heavily%20in%20the%20less%20costly%20alternative%20of%20shaping%20public%20opinion%20rather%20than%20outright%20high-handed%20methods%20%E2%80%93%20all%20the%20while%20pretending%20to%20be%20democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20India%2C%20the%20spin%20dictators%20co-opt%20media%20owners%2C%20bosses%2C%20and%20journalists%20as%20allies%20and%20use%20them%20for%20favourable%20publicity%20for%20themselves%2C%20the%20book%20says.%20They%20do%20it%20by%20wearing%20them%20down%20with%20lawsuits%20for%20tax%20violation%20and%20by%20arbitrary%20%E2%80%98pseudo-technical%E2%80%99%20means.%20(In%20India%2C%20the%20preferred%20method%20is%20financial%20harassment%20of%20owners%20via%20tax%20raids%20or%20blocking%20government%20advertisements).%20The%20spin%20dictators%20thus%20build%20a%20%E2%80%98devoted%E2%80%99%20pro-regime%20media%20even%20while%20allowing%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20to%20do%20critical%20stories.%20This%20tends%20to%20further%20enhance%20the%20dictator%E2%80%99s%20liberal%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20authors%2C%20spin%20dictators%20hold%20fairly%20free%20elections%20and%20allow%20the%20opposition%20to%20field%20candidates%20to%20create%20an%20impression%20of%20full%20democracy.%20But%20the%20opposition%20hardly%20gets%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%20Fund%20crunch%2C%20adverse%20media%20treatment%2C%20and%20outright%20harassment%20make%20their%20chances%20of%20victory%20%E2%80%98zero%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proportion%20of%20fear%20dictatorships%2C%20the%20authors%20say%2C%20has%20falled%20from%2060%25%20of%20the%20total%20in%20the%201970s%20to%20less%20than%2010%25%20since%202000%2C%20while%20that%20of%20spin%20dictatorships%20has%20risen%20from%2013%25%20to%2053%25.%20This%20qualitative%20shift%20has%20also%20been%20accompanied%20by%20what%20they%20call%20a%20%E2%80%98modernisation%20cocktail%E2%80%99%2C%C2%A0%20combining%20globalisation%20and%20economic%20and%20social%20modernisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20%3Cem%3ESpin%20Dictators%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20so%20Western-centric%20that%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20Cambodia%20and%20monarchies%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%20are%20out%20of%20its%20radar%2C%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20book%20will%20show%20that%20Modi%20has%20not%20only%20borrowed%20from%20their%20playbook%20but%20excelled%20in%20every%20respect%20by%20resorting%20to%20both%20fear%20and%20spin.%20He%20has%20already%20emerged%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3EVishwaguru%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20the%20spin%20dictators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20says%20spin%20dictators%20are%20adept%20in%20post-modern%20propaganda%20to%20show%20off%20their%20competence%20and%20leadership%20skills.%20They%20repeatedly%20appear%20on%20TV%20and%20other%20media.%20But%20Modi%20has%20outpaced%20them.%20Every%20public%20event%20Modi%20must%20inaugurate.%20Every%20Vande%20Bharat%20train%20he%20must%20flag%20off.%20Never%20mind%20how%20much%20a%20Modi%20function%20costs%20to%20the%20exchequer.%20An%20RTI%20reply%20said%20Rs.%201.48%20crore%20was%20spent%20on%20Thiruvananthapuram%20Vande%20Bharat%20function.%20Together%20with%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20function%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fexpensive-vande-bharat-flag-offs-southern-railways-spent-rs-26-crore-179696%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demailhttps%3A%2F%2Fepaper.telegraphindia.com%2F%5C%22%3Ecost%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rs%202.60%20crore%20to%20Southern%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F30174056%2F2022_9img30_Sep_2022_PTI09_30_2022_000068B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F30174056%2F2022_9img30_Sep_2022_PTI09_30_2022_000068B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F30174056%2F2022_9img30_Sep_2022_PTI09_30_2022_000068B-300x151.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F30174056%2F2022_9img30_Sep_2022_PTI09_30_2022_000068B-1024x516.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-622167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22605%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20flags%20off%20the%20Gandhinagar-Mumbai%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20train%2C%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20September%2030%2C%202022.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%20via%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20cheetah%20Modi%20must%20release%20in%20Kuno.%20Never%20mind%20one-third%20of%20them%20have%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Feighth-cheetah-dies-in-kuno%5C%22%3Edied%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20must%20figure%20prominently%20in%20every%20state%20government%20display%20advertisement%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20chief%20ministers.%20Now%20even%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20of%20Maharashtra%20has%20joined%20the%20hail%20Modi%20club%20(see%20the%20ads%20in%20the%20newspapers%20on%20July%2016).%20Every%20Ayush%20outlet%20should%20display%20a%20Modi%20hoarding%20at%20the%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3EThree%20More%20Cheetahs%20Have%20Neck%20Infections%3B%20Expert%20Says%20Last%20Cheetah%20Death%20%E2%80%98Potentially%20Avoidable%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2015%20central%20schemes%20have%20been%20named%20after%20%E2%80%98PM%E2%80%99.%20Sample%20a%20few%3A%20PM%20Swanidhi%2C%20PM%20Sadak%20Yojana%2C%20PM%20Pranam%2C%20PM%20Shri.%20The%20latest%20to%20enter%20the%20%E2%80%98PM%E2%80%99%20club%20is%20PMSSM%2C%20a%20renamed%20scheme%20launched%20during%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20rule.%20Now%2C%20perhaps%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20name%20directly%20figures%20in%20a%20central%20scheme%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fstudents-from-across-india-to-be-sent-to-modis-school-for-prerna-8649398%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAnnouncing%2520this%2520on%2520Tuesday%252C%2520the%2Cthe%2520central%2520and%2520state%2520governments%5C%22%3EModi%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20homilies%20to%20the%20members%20at%20a%20special%20function%20after%20the%20BJP%20national%20executive%20meeting%20is%20the%20highlight%2C%20not%20its%20deliberations%20as%20such.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20national%20executive%20was%20a%20vibrant%20body%20where%20half%20a%20dozen%20senior%20leaders%20debated%20party%20policies.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20brand%20Modi%20is%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpin%20dictators%2C%20authors%20say%2C%20seek%20to%20exploit%20international%20institutions%20to%20gain%20strategic%20leverage.%20For%20Modi%2C%20diplomacy%2C%20shorn%20of%20jargon%2C%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20his%20domestic%20policy%20of%20all-out%20persona%20build-up.%20Or%20call%20it%20Vishwaguru.%20To%20his%20credit%2C%20he%20has%20quite%20successfully%20marketed%20himself%20as%20an%20avowed%20democrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20skilfully%20takes%20advantage%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20market%20clout%20and%20its%20role%20as%20a%20deterrent%20to%20China.%20This%20enabled%20him%20to%20blunt%20the%20repeated%20criticism%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Fus-report-lists-significant-human-rights-abuses-india-2023-03-20%2F%5C%22%3Ehuman%20rights%20violations%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20decline%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Frsf-press-freedom-index-india%5C%22%3Epress%20freedom%20index%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Similarly%2C%20Modi%20sticks%20to%20the%20government-to-government%20mode%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20high-value%20defence%20deals%20%E2%80%94%20again%2C%20an%20effective%20lever%20to%20silence%20the%20critics%20of%20his%20authoritarian%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20how%20the%20Modi%20regime%20maintains%20its%20vice-like%20grip%20on%20every%20arm%20of%20the%20administration%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpin%20dictators%2C%20authors%20say%2C%20use%20religion%20to%20enhance%20their%20clout.%20But%20Modi%20made%20Hindutva%20and%20religious%20hatred%20the%20foundation%20of%20his%20vote%20base%20and%20cadre%20power.%20It%20is%20this%20Hindutvaisation%20of%20the%20community%20that%20helps%20the%20BJP%20retain%20power%20in%20its%20core%20states%20like%20Gujarat%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20way%20Modi%20tamed%2C%20made%20dormant%2C%20or%20weaponised%20watchdog%20bodies%20like%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%2C%20Central%20Vigilance%20Commission%2C%20Central%20Information%20Commission%2C%20National%20Statistical%20Office%2C%20and%20Lokpal.%20A%20look%20at%20the%20CAG%20reports%20shows%20how%20restrained%20and%20cautious%20it%20has%20been%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Centre%20while%20going%20the%20whole%20hog%20against%20the%20irregularities%20by%20the%20opposition%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEvery%20law%20like%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20has%20been%20tweaked%20to%20provide%20more%20punitive%20powers%20to%20the%20executive%2C%20enabling%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20imprison%20political%20rivals.%20Of%20late%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20become%20more%20liberal%20in%20granting%20bail.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELuckily%20for%20democracy%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20frustrated%20the%20executive%E2%80%99s%20moves%20to%20induct%20political%20favourites%20at%20crucial%20positions%20in%20the%20judiciary%20by%20striking%20down%20the%20National%20Judicial%20Appointments%20Commission%20(NJAC)%20Act.%20But%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20collegium%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20for%20judges%20are%20often%20delayed%20or%20killed%20by%20the%20government%20if%20the%20persons%20chosen%20are%20not%20to%20its%20liking.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20regime%20took%20advantage%20of%20financial%20levers%20like%20tax-exempt%20status%20for%20non-profits%20to%20silence%20criticism%20by%20reputed%20think%20tanks%20like%20Central%20for%20Policy%20Research%20and%20the%20Independent%20Public%20Spirited%20Media%20Foundation%20(a%20major%20donor%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%202016%20to%202019).%20The%20law%20on%20foreign%20contributions%20(FCRA)%20has%20also%20been%20similarly%20weaponosed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20established%20an%20effective%20system%20of%20informal%20liaison%20between%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2FCentral%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20local%20BJP%20leaders.%20The%20former%20pass%20on%20cases%20of%20%E2%80%98irregularities%E2%80%99%20by%20opposition%20leaders%20which%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20could%20make%20use%20of%20against%20them.%20The%20local%20leaders%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20provide%20political%20support%20to%20ED%E2%80%99s%20actions%20by%20launching%20public%20protests.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESystematic%20tweaking%20of%20the%20textbooks%20and%20extensive%20publicity%20of%20PM%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMan%20Ki%20Baat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20been%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20generation%20of%20Hindutvised%2C%20hate-filled%20future%20voters.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20achievement%20has%20been%20building%20a%20permanent%20ready-to-support%20system%20which%20has%20begun%20working%20on%20its%20own%20momentum.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20PMO%20or%20J.P.%20Nadda%E2%80%99s%20office%20had%20to%20prod%20the%20drum%20thumpers%20and%20supporters%20on%20how%20they%20should%20react%20to%20opposition%20attacks.%20Now%2C%20they%20respond%20on%20their%20own%20without%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fintricate-design-of-right-wing-propaganda-in-india%5C%22%3Emulti-level%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20instant%20response%20encompasses%20social%20media%2C%20films%