0Monday%2C%20July%2024%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Jal%20Shakti%20said%20that%20so%20far%20according%20to%20data%20provided%20by%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%2C%20out%20of%2019.46%20crore%20rural%20households%20in%20the%20country%2C%20approximately%2012.57%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20or%2064.61%25%20%E2%80%93%20households%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20tap%20water%20supply%20in%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%20of%20announcement%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20in%20August%202019%2C%203.23%20crore%20(17%25)%20rural%20households%20were%20reported%20to%20have%20tap%20water%20connections%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20reply%20provided%20by%20the%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Jal%20Shakti%2C%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20States%2F%20UTs%20as%20on%2015.07.2023%2C%20additional%209.34%20Crore%20rural%20households%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20tap%20water%20connections%20under%20JJM.%20Thus%2C%20as%20on%2015.07.2023%2C%20out%20of%2019.46%20Crore%20rural%20households%20in%20the%20country%2C%20approx.%2012.57%20Crore%20(64.61%25)%20households%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20tap%20water%20supply%20in%20their%20homes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShekhawat%20added%20that%20as%20on%20July%2015%2C%202023%2C%20nine%20states%20and%20UTs%2C%20140%20districts%2C%201%2C432%20blocks%2C%2082%2C250%20gram%20panchayats%20and%201%2C72%2C757%20villages%20are%20reported%20as%20having%20come%20under%20%E2%80%98Har%20Ghar%20Jal%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20scheme%20in%20partnership%20with%20state%20governments%20had%20promised%20to%20make%20provision%20of%20tap%20water%20supply%20to%20every%20rural%20household%20by%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20ministry%2C%20100%25%C2%A0%20of%20the%20rural%20households%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Dandra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu%2C%20Goa%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20have%20tap%20water%20supply%20as%20of%20July%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20reply%2C%20the%20states%20which%20have%20provided%20tap%20water%20to%20less%20than%2050%25%20of%20their%20rural%20households%20are%20West%20Bengal%20(34.23%25)%2C%20Jharkhand%20(38.64%25)%2C%20Rajasthan%20(40.96%25)%2C%20Kerala%20(49.73%25)%20and%20Lakshadweep%20(0)%2C%20as%20of%20July%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20data%20states%20that%20Delhi%20and%20Chandigarh%20do%20not%20have%20rural%20populations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-har-ghar-jal-by-2024%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20only%2075%25%20of%20households%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20water%20connection%20by%20March%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20delay%20was%20attributed%20in%20the%20report%20to%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20slowed%20operations%2C%20and%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20caused%20a%20shortage%20in%20raw%20materials%20for%20manufacturing%20metal%20pipes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690282254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F02213735%2FTap-water.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdeadline-approaching-govt-says-only-64-6-rural-households-covered-under-har-ghar-jhal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliament%20reply%20comes%20barely%20seven%20months%20after%20the%20government%20had%20announced%20in%20its%20year-end%20review%20that%20'Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20is%20on%20track%20t