0August%209%2C%202004%20and%20one%20from%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%201972%2C%20was%20allegedly%20burnt%20alive%20by%20Kuki%20militants%20in%20this%20village.%20Photos%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20show%20only%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20skull%2C%20and%20the%20family%20claims%20it%20belongs%20to%20Ibetombi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIbetombi%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20S.%20Churachandra%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20two%20houses%20in%20Serou%2C%20and%20my%20mother%20used%20to%20live%20in%20the%20other%20house.%20Violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20and%20later%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%20May%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20finally%20decided%20to%20visit.%20This%20incident%20happened%20a%20day%20before%20his%20visit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20family%20filed%20an%20FIR%20in%20the%20Sugnu%20police%20station.%20The%20FIR%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20indicates%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20unknown%20armed%20miscreants%20suspected%20to%20be%20Kuki%20militants%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20the%20crime.%20Sub-inspector%20H.%20Amitkumar%20Singh%20of%20the%20Kaching%20police%20station%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20investigating%20officer%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lists%20the%20following%20charges%3A%20IPC%20Sections%20148%20(rioting%20armed%20with%20a%20deadly%20weapon)%3B%20149%20(all%20members%20of%20an%20unlawful%20assembly%20guilty%20of%20an%20offence%20committed%20in%20the%20prosecution%20of%20a%20common%20object)%3B%20295A%20(outraging%20religious%20feelings%20by%20insulting%20religious%20beliefs%20or%20religion)%3B%20302%20(murder)%3B%20307%20(attempt%20to%20murder)%3B%20326%20(voluntarily%20causing%20grievous%20hurt%20by%20dangerous%20weapons)%3B%20400%20(gang%20of%20dacoits)%3B%20427%20(mischief%20for%20causing%20damage%20of%20the%20value%20of%2050%20rupees%20or%20more)%3B%20436%20(mischief%20by%20fire%20or%20explosive%20substance)%3B%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%3B%20and%2034%20(joint%20liability%20of%20persons%20for%20acts%20done%20in%20furtherance%20of%20common%20intention).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%20i.e.%2028%2F05%2F2023%20at%20about%2002%3A40%20am%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20unknown%20armed%20miscreants%20suspected%20to%20be%20Kuki%20militants%20attacked%20the%20Sugnu%20Police%20Station%2C%20Kakching%20District%2C%20Manipur%20from%20different%20angles%20with%20heavy%20volume%20of%20firing%20from%20their%20sophisticated%20weapons.%E2%80%9D%20It%20further%20explains%20that%20the%20security%20personnel%20at%20Sugnu%20police%20station%20were%20already%20on%20maximum%20alert%2C%20and%20they%20retaliated%20to%20protect%20the%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151418%2FIMG_4144.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151418%2FIMG_4144.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151418%2FIMG_4144-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151418%2FIMG_4144-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664979%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA.P.J.%20Abdul%20Kalam%20honouring%20S.%20Churachand.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20incident%2C%20suspected%20armed%20Kuki%20militants%20attacked%20security%20personnel%20discharging%20their%20duties%20at%20different%20locations%20and%20check%20posts.%20The%20Kuki%20militants%20and%20their%20supporters%20also%20attacked%20Meitei%20villagers%20in%20different%20locations%2C%20resulting%20in%20damage%20to%20many%20houses%20and%20valuable%20properties%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20under%20Sugnu%20PS%20jurisdiction%2C%20the%20FIR%20states.%20The%20indiscriminate%20firing%20by%20the%20unknown%20armed%20Kuki%20militants%20towards%20security%20personnel%20and%20villagers%20resulted%20in%20casualties%20and%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20unknown%20Meitei%20young%20people%20organised%20a%20mob%20that%20damaged%20houses%20and%20properties%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community.%20The%20situation%20was%20eventually%20brought%20under%20control%20by%20security%20personnel%20around%205%3A50%20pm.%20Consequently%2C%20a%20suo%20moto%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20the%20unknown%20armed%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIbetombi%E2%80%99s%20family%20claims%20that%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20police%20so%20far.%20The%20FIR%20was%20registered%20on%20May%2028%20at%206%3A15%20pm%2C%20and%20now%20almost%20two%20months%20have%20passed%20with%20no%20investigation.%20Ibetombi%20never%20imagined%20that%20the%20riots%20would%20escalate%20to%20such%20an%20extent%2C%20her%20son%20said.%20The%20day%20before%20her%20death%2C%20the%20family%20had%20lunch%20together%2C%20and%20Churachandra%20cooked%20her%20favourite%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Churachand%20remembered%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20told%20me%20that%20this%20would%20not%20escalate%20to%20the%20point%20of%20killing%20each%20other%20and%20that%20things%20would%20be%20fine%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20I%20never%20thought%20she%20would%20be%20burnt%20alive%20the%20very%20next%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20not%20only%20did%20the%20militants%20attack%20Meitei%20villages%2C%20they%20also%20attacked%20the%20Sugnu%20police%20station%2C%20resulting%20in%20casualties%20amongst%20the%20security%20personnel.%20The%20community%20is%20also%20disappointed%20with%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20the%