%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmyanmar-govt-in-exile-asks-refugees-in-india-to-stay-away-from-political-ethnic-conflicts%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0earlier%2C%20several%20political%20leaders%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20community%20have%20accused%20Myanmarese%20military%20groups%20of%20supporting%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20against%20persons%20belonging%20to%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20majority%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20share%20a%20porous%20border%20with%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Chin%20state.%20The%20Kukis%20and%20Mizos%20share%20a%20common%20ancestry%20with%20the%20Chins%20of%20Myanmar%20and%20inhabit%20that%20contiguous%20landmass%20across%20the%20international%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20India%20and%20Myanmar%20have%20a%20free%20movement%20regime%20(FMR)%20in%20place%20within%2016%20kms%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border.%20However%2C%20this%20has%20been%20temporarily%20suspended%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20groups%20have%20been%20claiming%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20state%20that%20even%20large-scale%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigration%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar%20has%20been%20playing%20a%20part%20in%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%20in%20the%20state.%20Even%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20accused%20Kukis%20in%20Churachandpur%20of%20illegally%20sheltering%20immigrants%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20also%20angered%20Kukis%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2015%2C%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20government-in-exile%2C%20the%20National%20Unity%20Government%20(NUG)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmyanmar-govt-in-exile-asks-refugees-in-india-to-stay-away-from-political-ethnic-conflicts%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20Myanmarese%20citizens%2C%20who%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Ctemporarily%20sheltering%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20due%20to%20the%20military%20crack