0Kerala%20belt.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pandemic%20gave%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20research%20how%20agricultural%20waste%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20disposable%20tableware.%20We%20came%20across%20paddy%20straw%20as%20a%20raw%20material.%20This%20agri-waste%2C%20if%20left%20in%20fields%20leads%20to%20stubble%20burning%2C%20contributing%20to%20yet%20another%20environmental%20crisis.%20We%20wanted%20to%20utilise%20this%20waste%20in%20valuable%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2020%20months%20of%20improvising%20the%20products%2C%20the%20brothers%20started%20selling%20commercially%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20these%20products%20are%20made%20from%20agricultural%20waste%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20collect%20husk%20and%20rice%20grain%20from%20mills%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20and%20straw%20from%20farmers%20across%20Kerala%20belt.%20Then%20after%20heating%2C%20crushing%2C%20and%20mixing%20them%2C%20the%20raw%20materials%20are%20compressed%20and%20moulded%20into%20finished%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCoUjLJiyiyt%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCoUjLJiyiyt%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2