here%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20local%20organisation%20or%20NGO%20who%20might%20have%20been%20working%20in%20these%20communities%20for%20years%20and%20already%20have%20that%20relationship%20built%20with%20them.%20When%20they%20bring%20us%20in%2C%20there%20is%20that%20sense%20of%20respect%20and%20trust%20already%20established%20when%20we%20go%20in.%20On%20our%20end%2C%20we%20also%20spend%20time%20with%20people%20explaining%20to%20them%20what%20structure%20is%20going%20to%20come%20up%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20maintain%20costs%2C%20Anthill%20largely%20procures%20materials%20locally%20and%20employs%20local%20labour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20elements%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20designed%20are%20simple%20and%20basic%20like%20tires%20and%20metal%20drums%2C%20and%20engage%20in%20recycling%20and%20upcycling%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20sense%20to%20transport%20things%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Tripura.%20We%20procure%20materials%20locally%20because%20it%20saves%20cost%2C%20available%20locally.%20Where%20it%20becomes%20challenging%20is%20to%20ensure%20the%20quality%20that%20we%20want%20in%20these%20elements%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20overcome%20these%20concerns%2C%20we%20have%20a%20set%20of%20vendors%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20we%20transport%20these%20joineries%20from%20one%20central%20hub%20to%20wherever%20we%20are%20building%20playgrounds.%20Elements%20like%20tires%20and%20metal%2C%20we%20procure%20locally%20because%20those%20are%20like%20the%20bigger%20bulk%20of%20what%20we%20kind%20of%20use%20to%20design%20these%20playgrounds.%20Given%20we%20have%20now%20built%20playgrounds%20in%2022%20different%20states%2C%20we%20have%20identified%20vendors%20and%20all%20of%20these%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20as%20stated%20earlier%2C%C2%A0%20Anthill%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20take%20ownership%20of%20the%20playgrounds%20they%20build.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20just%20facilitators%20who%20are%20enabling%20the%20local%20community%20or%20the%20school%20to%20build%20a%20playground.%20We%20bring%20in%20funding%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20corporation%20and%20provide%20our%20expertise%20in%20how%20to%20construct%20the%20playground.%20But%20after%20those%20six%20days%20of%20intervention%2C%20our%20major%20role%20is%20complete%20in%20building%20the%20playground%20and%20we%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20this%20handover%20period%20is%20over%20one%20or%20three%20months%2C%20it%20varies%20based%20on%20where%20the%20playground%20is%20located.%20They%20often%20complete%20building%20the%20playground%20in%20six%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20last%20day%2C%20we%20do%20a%20quality%20check%20with%20the%20corporate%20who%E2%80%99s%20funding%20the%20project%20and%20the%20local%20headmaster%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20playground%20we%E2%80%99ve%20constructed%20meets%20all%20the%20basic%20quality%20measures.%20And%20then%20we%20proceed%20towards%20our%20adoption%20plan.%20We%20identify%20one%20community%20champion.%20It%20could%20be%20anyone%20from%20a%20headmaster%20to%20a%20teacher%20or%20an%20alumni%20of%20that%20school%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20building%20that%20playground%20and%20is%20happy%20to%20volunteer%20their%20time.%20We%20maintain%20correspondence%20with%20them.%20After%20one%20month%2C%20we%20contact%20them%20to%20do%20a%20basic%20check%20on%20how%20children%20are%20playing%20in%20these%20playgrounds.%20We%20have%20a%20questionnaire%20that%20they%20answer%20to%20help%20us%20assess%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20playground.%20We%20get%20both%20quantitative%20and%20qualitative%20feedback%20and%20whenever%20we%E2%80%99re%20building%20a%20new%20play%20element%2C%20we%20receive%20some%20extra%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20cl