ngita%20says%20that%20bio%20alternatives%20also%20save%20one-third%20costs%20of%20farmers%20as%20compared%20to%20chemical%20fertilisers.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20typically%20use%20two%20to%20three%20bags%20of%2050%20kg%20each%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20one%20acre%20of%20land.%20However%2C%20using%20bio-fertilisers%2C%20only%201%20litre%20is%20needed%2C%20which%20is%20a%20significantly%20smaller%20amount%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangita%20further%20informs%20that%20farmers%20should%20add%20bio-fertilisers%20within%20the%20first%20month%20of%20the%20sowing%20period%20for%20a%20better%20yield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20bio-fertilisers%2C%20less%20dosage%20of%20bio-pesticides%20and%20bio-fungicides%20is%20used.%20As%20microorganisms%20keep%20multiplying%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20to%20spray%20multiple%20times.%20This%20reduces%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20input%20costs%20by%20one-third%20and%20prevents%20them%20from%20compounding%20debts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangita%20has%20helped%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20farmers%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Punjab%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t